Open terminal of your choosing.
Find httpd package in yum repos.
Install httpd.
Start httpd. Verify that it's running.
Remove httpd.
Find nginx package in yum repos.
Find out which repo provides nginx package and install it.
Install nginx.
Start nginx. Verify that it's running.
